Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,interface.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we reset back to the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,identity transform when we're
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So now that we have our app
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,acting playfully, let's talk
