Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To do that, we'll support
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,dynamic type.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dynamic type is a technology on
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,iOS that provides both a set of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,text styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, headline, body,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,caption.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And user control over the size
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of those styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a few example apps, and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,this is with a default text size
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,set.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if the user preferred a
