Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So the text increases, and then
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,all the graphic around -- the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,bubbles around the messages
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Also the input field gets
