Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to our app, and let's take
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a look at making these two
