Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.93,0:34:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You could also verify that with
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.52,0:34:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the device bar on the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.69,0:34:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now we're in landscape
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.42,0:34:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,iPhone seven plus with regular
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.59,0:34:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,width and compact type.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.47,0:34:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So for any width compact type,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.18,0:34:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to add a variation,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.10,0:34:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,mark it as hidden, and there we
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.44,0:34:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.38,0:34:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And, if we switch over to
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.55,0:34:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,portrait, it appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.15,0:34:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Going back to landscape, it's
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.53,0:34:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.59,0:34:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. We need to add our text
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.69,0:34:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,view now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.19,0:34:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And, in order to do that, we
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.05,0:34:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,need a outer horizontal view.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.28,0:34:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We need some sort of horizontal
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.01,0:34:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,stack view for being able to
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.52,0:34:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,host the text view.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.00,0:34:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to select
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.98,0:34:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,everything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.11,0:34:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'm going to type text
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.23,0:34:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,view in the object outline
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.45,0:34:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,because I want to add that in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.08,0:34:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go ahead and embed the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.48,0:34:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,outer view using the embed and
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.19,0:34:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,stack button.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.89,0:34:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So it created a new stack view,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.67,0:34:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and we need to switch it over to
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.52,0:34:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,be -- that's vertical.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.69,0:35:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to switch it over to be
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.64,0:35:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,horizontal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.70,0:35:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything shrunk down because
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.22,0:35:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,also, since I embedded it into
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.61,0:35:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,new view, it got rid of my
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.91,0:35:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,constraints to the superview.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.52,0:35:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So we need to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.43,0:35:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,horizontal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.51,0:35:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go ahead and give it a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.30,0:35:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,standard spacing for the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.38,0:35:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,outermost one we just created.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.10,0:35:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we can add a new text
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.90,0:35:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,view.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.34,0:35:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll just go ahead and drag
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.80,0:35:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.09,0:35:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.14,0:35:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we need to rebuild the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.41,0:35:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,constraints to our superview for
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.91,0:35:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the outermost one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.55,0:35:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to go back to the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.82,0:35:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,pinning menu 10, 10, 10, 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.86,0:35:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the bottommost
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.50,0:35:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,constraint, if you remember --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.46,0:35:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll zoom in here -- is going to
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.11,0:35:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,be greater than or equal to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.97,0:35:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. And so this is what I want
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.03,0:35:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.61,0:35:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When we switch back to portrait,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.08,0:35:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,we actually have to do a similar
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.09,0:35:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,thing and hide the text view by
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.89,0:35:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a size class.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.58,0:36:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we can click on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.63,0:36:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go over to the hidden menu again
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.33,0:36:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and add a variation --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.58,0:36:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Of any width, regular height,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.56,0:36:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and then mark it as hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.74,0:36:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we have the look that we
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.82,0:36:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,want.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.52,0:36:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.01,0:36:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So use the stack view, when you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.15,0:36:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,can, for all your layouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.32,0:36:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Alignment, distribution,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.32,0:36:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,spacing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.87,0:36:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are properties that will
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.72,0:36:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,get you there, including
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.69,0:36:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,nesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.47,0:36:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Add just a few constraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.88,0:36:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We only noticed it needed aspect
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.87,0:36:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,ratio constraint to get the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.86,0:36:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,proportion.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.47,0:36:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So you only need a few
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.31,0:36:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,constraints to get you a little
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.37,0:36:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,bit extra if you have some
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.77,0:36:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,requirements like the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.58,0:36:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,proportion.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.68,0:36:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The hidden property in Xcode 9
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.43,0:36:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is size classable, which is
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.08,0:36:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,great.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.39,0:36:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go ahead and use it, and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.83,0:37:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it works great with stack view,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.48,0:37:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because stack view will collapse
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.30,0:37:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,hidden subviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.87,0:37:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And best of all, varying by size
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.34,0:37:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,class with the hidden property
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.33,0:37:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is backwards deployable.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.52,0:37:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.40,0:37:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in summary, we've looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.32,0:37:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,six techniques today, and this
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.78,0:37:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to add to your arsenal
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.19,0:37:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,for being able to build out your
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.31,0:37:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.05,0:37:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot wait to see what you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.04,0:37:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,build.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.84,0:37:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And today we looked at some
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.81,0:37:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,techniques for being able to do
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.35,0:37:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,dynamic layout within the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.88,0:37:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,runtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.84,0:37:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Things like dynamic type, as
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.30,0:37:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,well as layout techniques, for
